on Council|BTECs]].\n\n==Notable former pupils==\n*[[Jordan Pickford]], [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Everton F.C.|Everton]] and England<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/jordan-pickford-i-was-always-brave-my-brother-would-get-me-to-dive-on-tarmac-vj52wt22f|accessdate=24 January 2018|title=Jordan Pickford School}}</ref>\n*[[Ethan Robson]], professional footballer for [[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]]<ref name=\"SAFC\">{{cite web|title=Ethan Robson Profile|url=https://www.safc.com/players/1st-team/ethan-robson|publisher=Sunderland A.F.C.|accessdate=3 October 2017}}</ref>\n*[[Paul Coughlin]], cricketer\n*[[Bridget Phillipson]], [[Labour Party (UK)|Labour Party]] [[Member of Parliament]] (MP) for [[Houghton and Sunderland South (UK Parliament constituency)|Houghton and Sunderland South]] (2010\u2013present)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/news/local-news/houghton-sunderland-south-constituency-election-8650510|accessdate=5 September 2017|title=Bridget Phillipson: Houghton & Sunderland South constituency election results}}</ref>\n*[[Si King]], [[Hairy Bikers]] member<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.itv.com/news/tyne-tees/update/2014-07-24/washington-new-town-50-years-on|title=Si King reference|date=24 July 2014}}</ref>\n*[[Paul Thirlwell|Paul Thirwell]], Footballer\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://strobertofnewminster.co.uk/ St Robert of Newminster Catholic School official website]\n\n{{City of Sunderland}}\n{{Schools in Tyne and Wear}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Saint Robert of Newminster Catholic School}}\n[[Category:Secondary schools in the City of Sunderland]]\n[[Category:Catholic secondary schools in the Diocese of Hexham and Newcastle]]\n[[Category:Voluntary aided schools in England]]\n[[Category:International Baccalaureate schools in England]]\n[[Category:Washington, Tyne and Wear]]\n[[Category:Comprehensive schools in Tyne and Wear]]\n\n\n{{TyneandWear-school-stub}}\n{{RC-stub}}\n", "